237
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,040
[SPEAKER_01] I originalni hrvatski.

238
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:07,200
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ili recimo, evo tu sam, ja tu imam 66 kilo, sad imam 96 kilo.g.

239
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:10,160
